---
title: Greek-inspired Pork Kofta Gyros with chips, mint yoghurt sauce and tomato salad
description: Gyros is a popular street food that originated in Greece but which today is enjoyed around the world. It can consist of many components but usually will be found with flatbread, meat, and a variety of toppings. This particular gyros has salad, cooling mint yoghurt, and crispy chips.
